docs.title: About Me
docs.text: I am Max Bai, a Senior student in the Honors Engineering/Computer Science program at Charlotte Latin. I am especially interested in math and icomputer science. Outside of class, I participate in soccer. My favorite hobbies are skiing and sleeping. In the future, I hope to continue studying computer science and mathematics in the future.
